<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Founder Special | Refinery Aesthetics</title>

  <!-- ── OG / SOCIAL META ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <meta name="description" content="Lock in your Botox rate and hold it for a full year. The Refinery Aesthetics Founder Special is free to claim — no payment required. First 10 to complete their appointment win." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Founder Special | Refinery Aesthetics" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Lock in your Botox rate for a full year. Free to claim. First 10 to complete their appointment win the founding rate." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.refineryaestheticswi.com/founder-special" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Founder Special | Refinery Aesthetics" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Lock in your Botox rate for a full year. Free to claim — no payment required." />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --dark:    #1a1a1a;
      --gold:    #c8a96e;
      --gold-lt: #e2cfa5;
      --cream:   #f0ebe3;
      --tan:     #e0d6c8;
      --white:   #faf8f4;
      --muted:   #7a7168;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--white);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── NAV ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .site-nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      background: rgba(26,26,26,0.97);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 44px;
      height: 68px;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 3px;
      text-decoration: none;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .nav-logo-word {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--white);
    }
    .nav-logo-rule { width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.6; }
    .nav-logo-sub {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 8px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .nav-tag {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.35);
      padding: 7px 18px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .site-nav { padding: 0 24px; }
      .nav-tag { display: none; }
    }

    /* ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: var(--dark);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 32px 80px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% -10%, rgba(200,169,110,0.14) 0%, transparent 65%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 10% 110%, rgba(200,169,110,0.06) 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 90% 110%, rgba(200,169,110,0.06) 0%, transparent 55%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-bg-text {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(100px, 20vw, 260px);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: italic;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: rgba(200,169,110,0.04);
      white-space: nowrap;
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 680px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.32em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow::before,
    .hero-eyebrow::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 32px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
    .hero-kicker {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(13px, 1.6vw, 15px);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.55);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .hero-kicker span {
      color: var(--gold-lt);
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.3em;
      text-transform: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(52px, 8vw, 96px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold-lt); }
    .hero-h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 44px);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .hero-rule {
      width: 48px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.5;
      margin: 0 auto 32px;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: clamp(14px, 1.6vw, 16px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.65);
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto 48px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--dark);
      padding: 18px 52px;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      transition: background 0.25s, color 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .hero-note {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.28);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── URGENCY BANNER ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .urgency-bar {
      background: var(--gold);
      padding: 14px 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .urgency-bar p {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    /* ── HOW IT WORKS ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .how {
      background: var(--cream);
      padding: 100px 40px;
    }
    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 72px;
    }
    .section-eyebrow {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 54px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--dark);
    }
    .section-title em { font-style: italic; }
    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .step {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 52px 40px 48px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .step::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200,169,110,0.4), transparent);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .step:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
    .step-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 56px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.25;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .step-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .step-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .step-desc {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .how { padding: 70px 24px; }
    }

    /* ── VALUE PROP ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .value {
      background: var(--dark);
      padding: 100px 40px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .value::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 80% at 50% 50%, rgba(200,169,110,0.07) 0%, transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .value-inner {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1px 1fr;
      gap: 0;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .value-divider {
      background: rgba(200,169,110,0.18);
      align-self: stretch;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .value-col {
      padding: 0 60px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .value-col:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
    .value-col:last-child { padding-right: 0; }
    .value-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .value-big {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 56px);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .value-big em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold-lt); }
    .value-small {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.45);
      max-width: 280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .value-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .value-divider { display: none; }
      .value-col { padding: 40px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12); }
      .value-col:last-child { border: none; }
      .value { padding: 70px 24px; }
    }

    /* ── CLOSING CTA ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .cta-section {
      background: var(--tan);
      padding: 100px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-section .section-title { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .cta-sub {
      font-size: 14.5px;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 460px;
      margin: 0 auto 48px;
    }
    .cta-fine {
      margin-top: 22px;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: rgba(122,113,104,0.85);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .cta-section { padding: 70px 24px; } }


    /* ── FOUNDER FORM ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #founder-form {
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 0 auto 8px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    /* ── Kajabi form style overrides ──────────────────────────────── */
    #founder-form .kajabi-subscribe-form,
    #founder-form form {
      background: transparent !important;
      border: none !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      box-shadow: none !important;
    }
    #founder-form .form-title,
    #founder-form h1, #founder-form h2, #founder-form h3,
    #founder-form label { display: none !important; }
    #founder-form input[type="text"],
    #founder-form input[type="email"],
    #founder-form input[type="tel"],
    #founder-form input:not([type="submit"]):not([type="checkbox"]):not([type="radio"]),
    #founder-form textarea {
      background: rgba(26,26,26,0.07) !important;
      border: 1px solid rgba(122,113,104,0.35) !important;
      border-radius: 0 !important;
      padding: 14px 18px !important;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif !important;
      font-size: 13.5px !important;
      font-weight: 300 !important;
      color: var(--dark) !important;
      outline: none !important;
      width: 100% !important;
      -webkit-appearance: none !important;
      margin-bottom: 10px !important;
      box-shadow: none !important;
    }
    #founder-form input::placeholder,
    #founder-form textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(26,26,26,0.35) !important; }
    #founder-form input:focus,
    #founder-form select:focus,
    #founder-form textarea:focus {
      border-color: rgba(122,113,104,0.7) !important;
      outline: none !important;
      box-shadow: none !important;
    }
    #founder-form input[type="submit"],
    #founder-form button[type="submit"],
    #founder-form .kajabi-button,
    #founder-form [class*="submit"],
    #founder-form [class*="Subscribe"],
    #founder-form [class*="subscribe"] {
      background: #b8955a !important;
      color: var(--dark) !important;
      border: 1px solid #b8955a !important;
      border-radius: 0 !important;
      padding: 15px 24px !important;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif !important;
      font-size: 11px !important;
      font-weight: 500 !important;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em !important;
      text-transform: uppercase !important;
      cursor: pointer !important;
      width: 100% !important;
      margin-top: 4px !important;
      transition: background 0.25s !important;
      -webkit-appearance: none !important;
      box-shadow: none !important;
    }
    #founder-form input[type="submit"]:hover,
    #founder-form button[type="submit"]:hover {
      background: var(--gold) !important;
      border-color: var(--gold) !important;
    }
    #founder-form .form-confirmation,
    #founder-form .confirmation-message,
    #founder-form [class*="success"],
    #founder-form [class*="confirm"] {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif !important;
      font-size: 13px !important;
      font-weight: 300 !important;
      color: var(--muted) !important;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em !important;
      background: transparent !important;
      border: none !important;
      padding: 16px 0 !important;
      text-align: center !important;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .footer {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      padding: 28px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.08);
    }
    html, body { margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .footer-social {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .footer-social a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 30px; height: 30px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.22);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.35);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer-social a:hover {
      border-color: rgba(200,169,110,0.55);
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.45);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .footer-dot { color: rgba(200,169,110,0.4); margin: 0 10px; }
    .footer-loc { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 400; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(28px);
      transition: opacity 0.75s ease, transform 0.75s ease;
    }
    .fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .fade-up:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
    .fade-up:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }

    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-14px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .hero-eyebrow  { animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease 0.10s both; }
    .hero-kicker   { animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease 0.25s both; }
    .hero h1       { animation: fadeInDown 0.9s ease 0.35s both; }
    .hero-h2       { animation: fadeInDown 0.9s ease 0.45s both; }
    .hero-rule     { animation: fadeInDown 0.7s ease 0.55s both; }
    .hero-sub      { animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease 0.65s both; }
    .hero-cta-wrap { animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease 0.78s both; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="site-nav">
    <a href="https://www.refineryaestheticswi.com" class="nav-logo">
      <span class="nav-logo-word">Refinery</span>
      <div class="nav-logo-rule"></div>
      <span class="nav-logo-sub">Aesthetics</span>
    </a>
    <div class="nav-tag">Founder Special</div>
  </nav>

  <!-- URGENCY BAR -->
  <div class="urgency-bar" style="margin-top:68px;">
    <p><strong>Offer closes the day we open our doors.</strong></p>
  </div>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-text">Refinery</div>
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Startup Founder Special</p>
      <p class="hero-kicker">Botox prices are going up.<br><span>Your price per unit doesn't have to.</span></p>
      <h1>Lock in your<br><em>rate.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-h2">Hold it for a full year.</p>
      <div class="hero-rule"></div>
      <p class="hero-sub">Grab your offer now. It's free, no payment required. When we open, the first 10 people to schedule and complete their appointment win the founding rate for a full year.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta-wrap">
        <a href="#claim" class="btn-primary">Grab the Founder Special →</a>
        <p class="hero-note">Free to grab · No payment required</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="how">
    <div class="section-header fade-up">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">How It Works</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Simple as <em>three steps</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <p class="step-num">01</p>
        <div class="step-icon"></div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Grab the offer</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">Claim your Founder Special now. Free, no payment required. Even if you're already on our general list, grab it here so we know you're in.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <p class="step-num">02</p>
        <div class="step-icon"></div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Schedule your appointment</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">When we open our doors, you'll get the call. Book your first appointment. The race to 10 starts the day we open.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <p class="step-num">03</p>
        <div class="step-icon"></div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Complete your visit, win your rate</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">The first 10 people to complete their appointment lock in the founding rate for a full year. Show up, and it's yours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUE SPLIT -->
  <section class="value">
    <div class="value-inner">
      <div class="value-col fade-up">
        <p class="value-label">What you get</p>
        <p class="value-big">Your rate,<br><em>frozen.</em></p>
        <p class="value-small">As industry Botox costs rise, your per-unit price stays exactly where your first visit set it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-divider"></div>
      <div class="value-col fade-up">
        <p class="value-label">For how long</p>
        <p class="value-big"><em>One</em><br>full year.</p>
        <p class="value-small">12 months from your first appointment. All visits, the same rate. Unhurried care, every time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA + FORM -->
  <section class="cta-section" id="claim">
    <div class="section-header fade-up">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Ready to Begin</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Already on our list?<br><em>This one's different.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="cta-sub">The Founder Special is a separate offer. Grab it here. Free, no payment required. The first 10 people to schedule and complete their appointment when we open win the founding rate for a full year.</p>

    <div id="founder-form">
      <script src="https://www.refineryaestheticswi.com/forms/2149549938/embed.js"></script>
    </div>

    <p class="cta-fine">Free to claim · First 10 to complete their appointment win the rate</p>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer">
